APEROL SPRITZ prompted the pace in the two path, bid passing the three eighths, took a short lead between foes midway around the far turn, but lost the lead turning into the lane, and faded. KINDNESS IS FREE had to steady midway around the first turn, tracked inside, but was stymied while along the rail rounding the far turn, tipped out to the three path turning into the stretch, but did not threaten. ZULLY BELLA set the pace inside but yielded along the rail turning into the stretch.
